{"tid":773443,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要咁對我 明明我對你仲好過對我自己","createTime":"2018-08-09T13:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T14:02:04.000Z","uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c4db179316f3b8580031da37d60ea067726c61f4","tid":773443,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T13:50:24.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪毒撚性格加上樣衰<br />\n越黎越大個 身邊最親密既人一個個都離自己而去<br />\n明明付出左好多時間既fd<br />\n都慢慢疏遠同忽視我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最好個個朋友<br />\n我地年年都會送生日禮物<br />\n但佢今次居然連續兩年無送 <br />\n過多排就三年 今年應該都無行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仍然都有送比佢<br />\n我一直都以黎都當佢係最好朋友 係知己<br />\n好多野都淨係同佢講<br />\n之前去旅行除左寄postcard比個ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係寄比佢<br />\n仲要每次都會幫佢買手信<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但佢居然咁對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢一年覆我成日都hea覆<br />\n又成日唔覆 <br />\n搞到我已經唔好意思搵佢食飯睇戲傾訴<br />\n我一直以為做情侶相處唔到就玩完<br />\n但做朋友可以做成世<br />\n但原來朋友疏遠你 離開你係更加突然<br />\n拍拖起碼都會講句分手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉 仲傷心過之前失戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b1624bc6e7a75269b78d61caba5f1dae622f70","tid":773443,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T13:56:52.000Z","msg":"🍐⏱🍊🦆"},{"pid":"429044d26b2dd628b8f97fc99a6179c3c917d35f","tid":773443,"uid":171816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T13:59:42.000Z","msg":"因為佢其實根本好憎你"},{"pid":"a638586a2a411ff514b598fc3446b69f115d508a","tid":773443,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45b1624bc6e7a75269b78d61caba5f1dae622f70","tid":773443,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T13:56:52.000Z","msg":"🍐⏱🍊🦆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T13:59:56.000Z","msg":"我唔係鴨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" cla